    "extras": [
      "International bank cards usually do not work in Iran, so carry enough cash in EUR or USD and exchange at city sarrafi counters rather than the airport when possible.",
      "Snapp is the easiest taxi app in major cities, while VIP buses are comfortable, reserved-seat coaches that are often better value than short domestic flights.",
      "Dress modestly: women should keep a headscarf handy and everyone should avoid very short or sleeveless clothing in religious sites.",
      "Friday is the weekly holiday, so museums, banks and some bazaars may open late or close early; confirm hours the day before.",
      "Easy vegetarian dishes to look for: kashk-e bademjan, mirza ghasemi, adasi, ash-e رشته, falafel in the south and plenty of saffron rice sides."
